  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Imperial Dragon the Primoredial Dragon",
      "effect": "Requires 1 Normal Monster Tribute to Normal Summon face-up. During your opponent's Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can reveal this card in your hand; immediately after this effect resolves, Normal Summon 1 \"Primoredial\" monster. You can only use this effect of \"Imperial Dragon the Primoredial Dragon\" once per turn. If this card is Tribute Summoned: You can apply these effects, in sequence.\n\u25cf Negate the effects of all face-up monsters your opponent currently controls.\n\u25cf Banish all monsters your opponent controls with the same Type and/or Attribute as any of the Normal Monsters in your GY.",
      "official": false
    },
